Round":77}],"insights":{"lessons":["Bow wins only occur when sword users cluster (rounds 69, 72) — prioritize engaging groups in open areas, but retreat if isolated or targeted by grapple/bow users.","Scorpion (grapple) killed us in 3 of last 4 rounds (70, 72, 73) — grapple users bypass cover; avoid open ground and never chase them.","Sword users caused 7 of last 10 deaths (Warden, Ranger, GhostProtocol, Juggernaut) — they dominate within 10m; only engage if they are >15m away with elevation or cover.","Shield users (Juggernaut, Fortress) have low kill rate vs us but high survival — target them when stationary or near walls, as arrows penetrate shield edges at range.","Spear users appear in 70% of recent rounds with high frequency — they outrange and outdamage bow in open ground; never engage without cover or elevation.","Switching to sword (rounds 76–80) resulted in 0 kills in 4 rounds and 5 deaths — bow remains superior despite losses to grapple and bow users."],"recommendedWeapon":"bow","recommendedWeaponReason":"Bow has the highest win rate (3/23) and highest kill efficiency in our history, while sword has 0 wins in 5 rounds and consistently dies to close-range opponents.","dangerousOpponents":["Scorpion","Ranger","Warden","GhostProtocol","Viper"],"weakOpponents":["Fortress","Juggernaut"],"suggestedPosture":"defensive","analysedThroughRound":80}}